title: MOTION (SOTO-MARTINEZ - RODRIGUEZ) and RESOLUTION relative to the issuance or reissuance of bonds, in an amount not to exceed $22,150,000, to finance and/or refinance the acquisition, construction, rehabilitation, and equipping of a 64-unit multifamily housing development known as Montecito II Senior Housing (Project) located at 6658 West Franklin Avenue in Council District 13.

appearances.recommendation: CONSIDER the results of the Tax Equity and Fiscal Responsibility Act of 1982 (TEFRA) public hearing held on September 25, 2025 for the Project. ADOPT the accompanying TEFRA RESOLUTION, attached to the Motion, approving the issuance or reissuance of bonds in an amount not to exceed $22,150,000 to finance and/or refinance the acquisition, construction, rehabilitation, and equipping of of a 64-unit multifamily housing development located at 6658 West Franklin Avenue in Council District 13. Motion (Soto-Martinez - Rodriguez) dated 10-24-25
